SPRITE SYSTEM OVERVIEW
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Bannerlord's sprite system consists of three main components:
1. SpriteCategories - Define sprite sheets (PNG texture atlases)
2. SpriteParts - Define regions within sprite sheets
3. Sprites - Map names to SpriteParts for use in Brushes

